  "text": "The influence of petroleum hydrocarbon on soil urease was shown in Figure 1 . The activity of urease was enhanced corresponding to increase the concentration of the crude oil. Soil urease activity showed a significantly negative correlation (P=0.002), which could be used as the most sensitive indicator of petroleum contamination [CITATION_1] .",
